{
  "stem": "19921.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was the last time I was in Poland, was in-- in my city, was 1945.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- the-- the in the town itself, there was all kind of little industries and businesses, but the surrounding area was mostly farmers and forests.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But mostly farmers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were fruit farmers and all other farming-- vegetables, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family consisted of my father, my mother, and I had five brothers originally.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One of them, unfortunately, passed away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was 1932, as far as I remember. 1932, yes-- that was the oldest one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was a businessman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother, of course, was a housewife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- as far as the household itself, it was a religious-- a religious home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was no conservatism in Europe, but it was orthodox-- strict orthodox and just plain orthodox.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's where I came from, from a orthodox family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Which could be easily imagined the way we have here conservatism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as far as the people living in town, it was a very nice community, actually.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I myself, as far as I remember-- don't forget, we're talking here way back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I myself did not feel any antisemitism in city itself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was going to a Catholic school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And because schools were public and were run by the government, the majority were Catholic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was a Catholic school, but it was not conducted by priests or such.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Religion was taught in school, and each denomination-- domination had their own preachers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In other words, the Catholic had a priest, and it was conducted every, every week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was conducted two hours a day-- a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the Jewish people had-- they did not have a rabbi, but we had a religious-- a religion-- professor of religion.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
